+# Currency Exchange App - New Design Implementation

+## Overview
+
+The app has been redesigned with a modern, card-based UI layout. The new design focuses on clarity,
+better visual hierarchy, and improved user experience while maintaining all core functionality.
+
+## Key Design Changes
+
+### 1. **Color Scheme**
+
+- **Background**: Light blue-grey (`#E8EEF2`) for a softer, more professional look
+- **Cards**: Pure white (`#FFFFFF`) with rounded corners for content sections
+- **Primary Button**: Bright blue (`#2196F3`) for clear call-to-action
+- **Text Colors**:
+ - Primary: Dark grey (`#2C3E50`)
+ - Secondary: Mid grey (`#5D6D7E`)
+ - Placeholder: Light grey (`#BDC3C7`)
+
+### 2. **Layout Structure**
+
+- **No Header Bar**: Removed the blue header bar; title is now integrated into the page
+- **No Profile Icon**: Removed as requested
+- **No Bottom Navigation**: Single-page design without tabs
+- **No Flags**: Currency display is text-only, no flag icons
+
+### 3. **Balance Display**
+
+- **Card-Based Layout**: Balances shown in a single white card with dividers
+- **Horizontal Layout**: Up to 3 currencies displayed side by side
+- **Clean Typography**: Currency code on top, balance below
+- **Vertical Dividers**: Subtle lines separating each currency
+
+### 4. **Exchange Section**
+
+- **Card-Based Design**: SELL and RECEIVE sections each in their own white card
+- **Improved Spacing**: More breathing room between elements
+- **Better Labels**: Clear "SELL" and "RECEIVE" labels at top of each card
+- **Swap Icon**: Circular white badge with exchange arrows (⇅) between cards
+- **Currency Selector**: Pill-shaped grey background for better visibility
+- **Amount Input**: Larger, bolder text for better readability
+
+### 5. **Live Rate Display**
+
+- Centered text showing current exchange rate
+- Format: "Live rate: 1 [SELL_CURRENCY] = [RATE] [BUY_CURRENCY]"
+- Updates dynamically as user types
+
+### 6. **Submit Button**
+
+- **Modern Design**: Large, full-width rounded button
+- **Bold Blue**: Eye-catching color (`#2196F3`)
+- **Clear Label**: "SUBMIT" in bold white text
+- **Height**: Increased to 56dp for better touch target
+
+### 7. **Network Status**
+
+- **Inline Warning**: Shows below title when offline
+- **Warning Icon**: ⚠️ emoji with yellow text
+- **Network Dialog**: Maintained with retry functionality
+
